BankTransactionSubfamily.description:
Specifies the bank transaction subfamily. Some possible ISO 20022 compliant values are: 
 For CustomerCardTransactions family: CashDeposit, CashWithdrawal, SmartCardPayment, PointOfSalePaymentDebitCard, CreditCardPayment, CrossBorderCreditCardPayment, CrossBorderCashWithdrawal, InternalBookTransfer, PrincipalPayment, LoanAdvance,
